						               													<description>Welcome to Operaci&amp;oacute;n Signo! A game in which everyone wins or everyone loses. Your objective will be to solve different tasks together with your classmates trying to reach an agreement. Will they manage to finish all the tasks on time?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The dynamic is simple: Cards with requirements will be revealed that will have to be met as quickly as possible, ordering cards with symbols and numbers. The challenge? Coordinate with your classmates to beat the clock.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A cooperative game for 2 to 8 players (a lot) in which they will have to solve different puzzle-like tasks together as fast as they can (possibly fighting and yelling in the middle) to complete everything before they run out time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game has two ways to play:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     One a little (very little) calmer in which someone takes the role of leader who explains the tasks and it will be key to listen to that person and respond quickly.&amp;#10;     And another more chaotic way in which everyone solves their tasks in the middle of fighting so that they don't take away the cards they need.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
